div.span: Assertive Logisticians are Introverted, Observant, Thinking, Judging and Assertive. Logisticians are practical and fact-minded individuals, whose reliability cannot be doubted. They’re reserved yet willful, with a rational outlook on life, composing their actions carefully.
Sentinels are cooperative and practical, embracing and creating order, security, and stability. They’re hard-working, meticulous, and traditional, preferring to stick to their plans.
Confident Individualists prefer doing things alone, choosing to rely on their own skills and instincts instead of seeking contact with other people. They know what they are good at.
Likely prefers fewer, yet deep and meaningful, social interactions and feels drawn to calmer environments.
Likely pragmatic and down-to-earth, with a strong focus on what is happening or very likely to happen.
Likely focuses on objectivity and rationality, putting effectiveness above social harmony.
Likely decisive, thorough, and highly organized. Values clarity and prefers planning to spontaneity.
Likely self-assured, even-tempered, and resistant to stress, refusing to worry too much.
